{"tid":1367014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認清事實：香港人想要民主，最重要力量係要拉攏大陸人推倒共產黨...","createTime":"2019-07-26T06:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T14:52:54.000Z","uid":107611,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93c5e5185c4a132acb8541108c7600bf558bc02e","tid":1367014,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:36:19.000Z","msg":"就好似其中位巴打開呢個post一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人民绝不会独立，也不支持独立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1366824\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1366824</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（殘體字做文宣係方便佢地睇，日後共產黨倒台可以大力教育正體字）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我意思就係從呢個方向去走，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋都可以拉一派打一派，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人靠自己能力係未足夠，<br />\n（就算係撐港獨，但為咗民主唔可以跳咗打倒共產黨個step)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想有生之年有真民主，唔可以再自掃家前門前雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大力文宣"},{"pid":"1688661f985dc482851d9decd0f4add7de758c7f","tid":1367014,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"我地係時侯反攻上面網壇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真大陸帝征軍都被徵軍，我開始相信我地無野做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464ac26a67c0d0bfcc4a389149968f74c9cc0e05","tid":1367014,"uid":32391,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"我地要好似新加坡咁<br />\n我地唔係想獨立 係比共產黨趕出去"},{"pid":"e75fcf18a80a0394aea8bfa0e0d4fe88a6c3711b","tid":1367014,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"464ac26a67c0d0bfcc4a389149968f74c9cc0e05","tid":1367014,"uid":32391,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"我地要好似新加坡咁<br />\n我地唔係想獨立 係比共產黨趕出去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:56:52.000Z","msg":"如果係梁振英年代前果種自治，我其實唔介意"},